    {
      "id": 117265,
      "post_number": 5,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-06-03T09:53:37.859Z",
      "cooked": "<p>top-10 <em>subjektiv</em> Woody (Allen Stewart Konigsberg - emri i vertete) :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Annie Hall (1977)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Manhattan (1979)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2005/11/24/match-point-film-i-woody-allen-2/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Match Point</a> (2005)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Manhattan Murder Mystery (1993)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>The purple rose of Cairo (1985)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2007/12/02/cassandras-dream-film-amerikan-nga-woody-allen-2/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Cassandra’s dream</a> (2007)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Shadows &amp; fog (1992)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Hannah and her sisters (1986)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2015/11/09/irrational-man-film-amerikan-me-regji-the-woody-allen-ose-dostojevski-for-dummies/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Irrational man</a> (2015)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://kinoditar.wordpress.com/2018/03/08/wonder-wheel-film-amerikan-me-regji-te-woody-allen/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Wonder wheel</a> (2017)</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Duhet te kem harruar ndonje…<br>\n(nderkohe qe nuk kam parë asnjehere “Interiors”, “Crimes and misdemeanors” apo “Another woman” per te cilet thuhet se jane sh sh te mirë)</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 117266,
      "post_number": 6,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-06-03T10:04:33.747Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Nuk e kam hiç qef kete film. Nga Oshima pelqej filmat e tij te parë te fillim viteve '60, <em>“Cruel Story of Youth”</em>, <em>“A Town of Love and Hope”</em>, <em>“The Sun’s Burial”</em>  apo <em>“Night and Fog in Japan”</em>.</p>\n<p>Tek te mevonshmit (vitet '70) ka shume manierizem : <em>“In the Realm of the Senses”</em>, <em><strong>“Empire of Passion”</strong></em> apo <em>“Merry Christmas, Mr. Lawrence”</em></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 4,
      "like_count": 0
    },
    {
      "id": 117267,
      "post_number": 7,
      "username": "STALKER",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/stalker/{size}/2135_2.png",
      "created_at": "2021-06-03T10:11:52.653Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Nuk eshte i vetmi : pothuaj te gjithe regjizoret-autorialë prodhimtarë (pothuaj nje film ne vit) si Rohmer, Cassavetes, Hong Sang-soo etj, pak a shume <em>\"nje teme i kane rene</em>\" (apo i bien)</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 2,
      "like_count": 0
    },
